programs.program:
as principal admin password "admin" do
set records = []
append to records with { name = "mike", date = "1-1-90" }
append to records with { name = "sandy", date = "1-1-90" }
append to records with { name = "dave", date = "1-1-85" }
local names = records
filtereach rec in names with equal(rec.date,"1-1-90")
filtereach rec in records with notequal(rec.date,"1-1-90")
append to records with names
return records
***

as principal admin password "admin" do
set x = []
append to x with "hello"
append to x with "there"
append to x with { x="oh my" }
set z = x
filtereach y in x with "0"
filtereach y in z with ""
append to x with z
return x
